content:
Hello,

After submitting my files for PSET 1, I noticed that after the "select file" button, the website states "Fakepath". However, the website also stated my code submitted. Would this be an issue or is this typical?
subject: "Fakepath" Shown On Submission

content:
That's typical. Whenever you upload a file to a website submission portal, it always hides the file path as to not reveal information about your PC file system to others (particularly to the owners of the website)
If it says submitted, you should be all good
